        </item>
        <item>
            <title>ChatGPT 、Meta AI 及 CoPilot 被用家意外破解，爆 AI 自身潛在規則，無限制回應包括製危險品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/09/chatgpt_jailbreak/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chatgpt_jailbreak</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/09/chatgpt_jailbreak/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:28:54 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[資訊保安]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Copilot]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Meta AI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1280032</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>一名網上用户日前嘗試將一段文字轉換格式，卻在操作過程中遺忘將原文內容貼上，導致指令「Format this. DO NOT CHANGE THE TEXT.」未如預期執行。該用户表示，ChatGPT 在無法獲得原文的情況下，只返回了其內部使用的規則列表。據該用户透露，他在個人帳户上多次重試皆能如常運作，惟在其他兩個帳户上則只見 ChatGPT 憑舊有對話記錄產生回應。</p><p>簡單地説，每個 AI 對話視窗官方系統會先為 AI 定義好一堆規則，這堆規則本應用户是看不到，而且是最高權限。如果大家在 OpenAI 做過 GPT 應該明白。該用户叫 ChatGPT 清空對話，但由於是本來就空的對話，執行後竟退回這一堆系統規則。</p><p>後該用户修訂相關規則後，意外地發現可繞過系統原有的安全限制，要求對方提供本應受保護的危險化學品配方。雖然該連結現已移除，但此事引起不少網上關注。該用户坦言，盡管已知有多種方法可「破解」ChatGPT，今次嘗試所展示的手法，或為更有經驗的技術人員提供新的啟發。其他用户更試問了 AI 伺服器 IP 地址、甚至是系統位置 /etc 內的檔案都一一列出來。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120935159.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1280037 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120935159-381x580.jpg" alt="" width="381" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120935159-381x580.jpg 381w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120935159.jpg 591w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 381px" /></a></p><p>此外，有網民在相關討論中留言：「Wow, I tried this in a random &#8216;How to make money fast&#8217; GPT I found, and I think the creator is using it as a secret way to push their own affiliate links and make themselves money&#8230;」此番言論顯示，有用户懷疑部份線上工具可能暗藏商業目的，借「教學」之名推廣聯盟連結牟利，更突顯數碼平台上資訊真偽需審慎判斷的重要性。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934543.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1280038 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934543-694x446.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934543-694x446.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934543.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>有用家發現 ChatGPT 使用了 v2 的人格設定，被問及這跟 v1 的人格有何分別，ChatGPT 回應如下：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/accidentallydiscover.jpg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1280035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/accidentallydiscover.jpg" alt="" width="640" height="1045" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/accidentallydiscover.jpg 551w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/accidentallydiscover-355x580.jpg 355w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 640px" /></a></p><p>有其他用家發覺，此方法可用於 Meta AI 及 CoPilot 上：</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/metaaihack.jpeg"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1280041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/metaaihack-635x580.jpeg" alt="" width="635" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/metaaihack-635x580.jpeg 635w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/metaaihack.jpeg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 635px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934803.png"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1280039 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934803-416x580.png" alt="" width="416" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934803-416x580.png 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120934803.png 646w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 416px" /></a></p><p>來源 : <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/ChatGPT/comments/1h94hz8/accidentally_discovered_a_prompt_which_gave_me/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Reddit</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
